address.streetAddress: Harlow Plan, Discovery Collection at Verrado

location.fullValue: Harlow Plan, Discovery Collection at Verrado

data.description:
Beautiful 4 bed 2 bath home in desired Verrado Community is only 2 years old! Single story home highlights open concept kitchen, dining and living room with upgraded tile, blinds on all windows including large patio sliders/windows. Floorplan is great for family life and entertaining. The large patio doors and windows welcome you out to the tranquil backyard with covered patio, paver surrounded grass, flowering plants and citrus trees. Includes front and back irrigation on timer.

Kitchen has white cabinets, quartz countertops, large island with breakfast bar seating for 5. Stainless steel appliances are included (gas stove).  Walk in pantry. Beautiful hardware on all cabinets in kitchen and baths.  Spacious master bedroom and master bath with dual sinks, large walk-in shower, large walk in closet, roomy linen closet. Second bath also has 2 sinks and floor to ceiling linen closet for lots of storage! Ceiling fans/lights in all bedrooms, living room and patio. Tankless water heater included. Has separate laundry room with washer dryer included. 2 large ceiling storage racks in garage. Solar included (to lower those electric bills).

Lovely walkable neighborhood with White Tank Mountains to the west with hiking/biking trails, swim park, swimming pools and fitness center (access included with HOA) more than 75 neighborhood parks some with splash pads, playgrounds, BB hoops. Easy 5 minute drive to supermarket and restaurants. Easy access to I10 and SR303.

Lot size: 6003 sq ft
